data.description: Warm Oasis for you and yours! This inviting retreat is situated on 1.15 acres and offers a spacious 2,735 sq ft living area, exceeding 3,587 sq ft overall! Vaulted ceilings, Plantation shutters, authentic Mexican tile welcome you as you are lead to the large Saltwater Pool, Roofed-over patio, fenced-in yard with no pond! The Master suite has dual walk-in closets and a large bathroom. Experience Loxahatchee's serene surroundings with all the possibilities of horses, boats, RVs, and more. This residence is a testament to comfort, sprawling space, and personal freedom--a Warm Oasis waiting to be embraced. Transferrable Home Warranty Included! Motivated ROOF - 2014, 2 New ACs 2023, New Insulation 2023 and Epoxy Garage Floor 2023
